EventItemActionText: This Introduction was Referred to Comm by Council to the Committee on Contracts

EventItemMatterName: Anti-graffiti task force.

EventItemMatterName: Curb cuts.

EventItemTitle: A Local Law to amend the administrative code of the city of New York, in relation to trap-neuter-return information and activities in the city of New York.
EventItemMatterName: Trap-neuter-return information and activities in NYC.

EventItemMatterName: Bus and subway fare evasion reporting.

EventItemMatterName: Exempting zero emission vehicles from idling restrictions.

EventItemActionText: This Resolution was Referred to Comm by Council to the Committee on Public Safety

EventItemMatterName: NYPD and the MTA to stop arresting people for committing minor infractions in the transit system.
